WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:04.000
Downloaded From www.AllSubs.org

00:00.105 --> 00:02.200
Shared by http://DJJ.HOME.SAPO.PT/

00:02.373 --> 00:04.682
LORNE: <i>A mystical pregnancy</i>
<i>right under my beak?</i>

00:05.133 --> 00:06.452
[GRUNTS]

00:09.373 --> 00:10.806
GUNN:
<i>You're a Power that was?</i>

00:11.013 --> 00:12.605
ANGEL:
<i>We've all been saved.</i>

00:13.573 --> 00:15.165
Hello.

00:15.853 --> 00:17.127
Bless you all for coming.

00:17.293 --> 00:20.729
I scrubbed the other one till my
fingers bled, but I couldn't get out the...

00:20.893 --> 00:22.565
- Fred?
- Blood.

00:22.733 --> 00:24.689
I can't believe Fred's evil.

00:24.853 --> 00:26.206
I'm so sorry.

00:27.013 --> 00:28.731
FRED:
<i>Jasmine's blood...</i>

00:28.893 --> 00:31.885
<i>... somehow it breaks her spell</i>
<i>when it mingles with ours.</i>

00:32.052 --> 00:33.725
Fred infected Angel. He's gone.

00:34.093 --> 00:37.051
We have to help the others.
We need more of Jasmine's blood.

00:37.213 --> 00:39.522
FRED: <i>He figured since Cordy</i>
<i>gave birth to Jasmine...</i>

00:39.693 --> 00:42.810
<i>... they might share a blood link</i>
<i>as well as a mystical one.</i>

00:42.973 --> 00:44.850
What are you doing to the...?

00:45.013 --> 00:47.447
WESLEY: Your wrist, you've cut it.
What happened to you?

00:47.613 --> 00:50.173
ANGEL: We hoped Cordy's blood
would have the same effect...

00:50.333 --> 00:51.891
...when we exposed you to it.

00:52.053 --> 00:54.521
- Thanks for nothing.
- I'm not leaving this hotel...

00:54.693 --> 00:56.331
...without my son.
- Hey.

00:58.533 --> 00:59.932
[YELLS]

01:01.013 --> 01:02.731
You're back with us now, Connor.

01:04.212 --> 01:07.091
They're here!
Come quick, they're here!

01:08.893 --> 01:10.485
Connor, you have to listen to us.

01:10.653 --> 01:13.087
Listen to you?
You're the ones who lie, who hate.

01:13.253 --> 01:14.845
- No...
- Jasmine's controlling you...

01:15.013 --> 01:17.129
...controlling your feelings.
- You're wrong...

01:17.293 --> 01:20.126
...about me, about her. Everything.

01:21.493 --> 01:23.848
But it doesn't matter
anymore what you say.

01:24.173 --> 01:26.846
We're going to tear you apart.

01:29.933 --> 01:33.892
Run! Get to the car.
Get out of here. I'll hold them off.

01:34.053 --> 01:37.011
Someone who knows the truth has
to live through this.

01:37.733 --> 01:40.088
- Go!
- Come on.

01:48.213 --> 01:52.001
CONNOR: I'm finally part of something.
I belong.

01:54.213 --> 01:55.931
I won't let anyone ruin that.

01:56.133 --> 01:57.486
[GRUNTS]

01:57.653 --> 01:58.927
I know, son.

